    "body": "> \ud83e\udd16 This comment was written by Coder Agent on behalf of Danielle Maywood \ud83e\udd16\n\nGood catch \u2014 those two tests did have the retry-and-re-fire pattern (the `toBeDefined` guard was vacuous, and the DOM assertions inside `waitFor` were the real retry triggers). While applying the fix I found the subscriber-registration timing that guard was accidentally load-bearing for, so the final shape is: `waitFor` for `API.templateVersionDynamicParameters` to be called, `act()` around the publish, then `waitFor` the assertion. Fixed in f2526f60b.\n",
